29479.name: Hinode
29479.description: I'm a succesosor artifact to solor observation satellite 'Yoko'. I observe phisics phenomenon related solar flare at the maxmum solor activity, solor colona or others. I have 3 types of scope; for visible light, X ray, extreme ultraviolet ray.

33492.description: I reglarly observe greenhous effect gas such CO2 or methane, almost over the earth. As a result of 3 and half years, I discovered relation of human activity and increasing greenhouse effect gas.
